function compareVersions(a,b){const pa=String(a||'0').split(/[.-]/).map(x=>/^\d+$/.test(x)?Number(x):x),pb=String(b||'0').split(/[.-]/).map(x=>/^\d+$/.test(x)?Number(x):x);for(let i=0;i<Math.max(pa.length,pb.length);i++){const x=pa[i]??0,y=pb[i]??0;if(typeof x==='number'&&typeof y==='number'){if(x!==y)return x>y?1:-1}else{const c=String(x).localeCompare(String(y),'de');if(c)return c>0?1:-1}}return 0}
